Package org.gvsig.remoteClient.sld.symbolizers

Interface Summary
ISLDSymbolizer Implements an interface for SLD symbolizers in order to define methods for them.
 

Class Summary
SLDLineSymbolizer Implements the LineSymbolizer element of an SLD implementation specification .
SLDMultiLineSymbolizer Implements a symbolizer which can contain more than one SLDLineSymbolizer at the same time
SLDMultiPointSymbolizer Implements a symbolizer which can contain more than one SLDPointSymbolizer at the same time
SLDMultiPolygonSymbolizer Implements a symbolizer which can contain more than one SLDPolygonSymbolizer at the same time
SLDMultiShapeSymbolizer Implements a symbolizer which can contain a SLDLineSymbolizer, an SLDPointSymbolizer and an SLDPolygonSymbolizer at the same time
SLDPointSymbolizer Implements the Point Symbolizer element of an SLD implementation specification .
SLDPolygonSymbolizer Implements the PolygonSymbolizer element of an SLD implementation specification.
